    dc:description "FIGURES 82 – 88. Billaea spp., heads of male in lateral view. 89 – 90. Abdomens in dorsal view. 82. B. micronychia sp. nov. 83. B. morosa Mesnil. 84. B. papei sp. nov. 85. B. setigera sp. nov. 86. B. steini (Brauer et Bergenstamm). 87. B. triangulifera (Zetterstedt). 88. B. verticalis sp. nov. 89. B. atkinsoni sp. nov. 90. B. chinensis sp. nov. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/288394/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.288395>
    dc:description "FIGURES 91 – 97. Billaea spp., heads of male in anterior view. 98 – 99. Abdomens in dorsal view. 91. B. micronychia sp. nov. 92. B. morosa Mesnil. 93. B. papei sp. nov. 94, 98. B. setigera sp. nov. 95. B. steini (Brauer et Bergenstamm). 96, 99. B. triangulifera (Zetterstedt). 97. B. verticalis sp. nov. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/288395/files/figure.png" ;
